{"word":"ῥίον","slug":"ῥίον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n92511\" key=\"r(i/on\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ῥίον</orth> [<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ῐ], <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen></foreign>, <sense id=\"n92511.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">any jutting part</tr_> of a mountain, whether upwards or forwards; hence, </sense> <sense n=\"1\" id=\"n92511.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">peak</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">περὶ ῥίον Οὐλύμποιο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:25\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.25</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:14:154\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.154</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:225\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">225</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ῥ. ὀρέων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:9:191\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.191</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ῥ. οὔρεος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0013.tlg003.perseus-grc1:139\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ h.Ap.\">h.Ap.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">139</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n92511.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">headland</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:3:295\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.295</biblScope> </bibl>; hence as pr. name of several places, esp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ῥ. Μολυκρικόν</foreign> and <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ῥ. Ἀχαϊκόν</foreign> at the mouth of the gulf of Corinth, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:86\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.86</biblScope> </bibl> (cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:84\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">84</biblScope> </bibl>). </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n92511.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> later, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">bay formed by a foreland</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0545.tlg001:15:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ael.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ NA\">NA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.3</biblScope></bibl>. (Perh. akin to <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ῥίς</foreign>, cf. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">Ness, Naze</tr_> with <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">nose.</tr_>)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}